net.sf.jclec.mo

Interface IMOPopulation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.sf.jclec.IPopulation, net.sf.jclec.util.random.IRandGenFactory, net.sf.jclec.ISystem, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MOStrategyContext

    public interface IMOPopulation
extends net.sf.jclec.IPopulation
    This interface specifies the required methods that context objects (implementations of IPopulation) should implement when solving multi-objective problems.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    1.0
    Author:
